(16246, 'buprenorphine hydrochloride', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Examples: Alcohol, benzodiazepines and other sedatives/hypnotics, anxiolytics, tranquilizers, muscle relaxants, general anesthetics, antipsychotics, gabapentinoids (gabapentin or pregabalin), and other opioids.', 'DailyMed'),
